source.name: OASAS Medicaid Recipient Trended Detail Profile
source.description: This profile shows the services received by Medicaid recipients, recipient counts, paid claim dollars, claim amounts, dollars per individual and dollars per unit of service for each detailed type of Medicaid chemical dependence services and for non-chemical dependence services received by the chemical dependence cohort.
